The '''chest''' is a thievable chest in the [[Isle of Souls Dungeon]] that requires level 28 [[Thieving]] to steal from. Each chest yields 150 [[experience]], and the chest's loot respawns instantly. This chest is the sole source of [[dark key]]s, which are used to loot the [[Dark Chest]] in the [[Crumbling Tower]] basement. It is possible to trigger a trap and get teleported out of the dungeon.

In order to save inventory space when looting the chest, it is recommended to bring a [[gem bag]] and [[herb sack]].

