===Success chance===
The chance of successfully opening the soul chest is -9% at level 1, and 60% at level 99, interpolating linearly in between. Carrying a [[lockpick]] increases the rate of success.{{CiteTwitter|author=Mod Ash|url=https://twitter.com/JagexAsh/status/1526998390491516931|date=18 May 2022|archiveurl=https://archive.ph/AR59A|archivedate=18 May 2022|quote=[Low/Highs for soul chest are] -23, 153, and the lockpick's doing +26.|notes=|name=|group=}}

If players fail to loot the chest, there is a 1 in 6 chance{{CiteTwitter|author=Mod Ash|url=https://twitter.com/JagexAsh/status/1450810611877793794|date=20 October 2021|archiveurl=https://archive.md/od3cd|archivedate=4 November 2021|quote=1/6 if you failed the thieving roll.}} to get teleported north-east of the dungeon entrance.

